{
  "stem": "20405.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was so cold, so cold that every 30 minutes, we have to get up and go and leg for pain.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do they call them, every 30 minutes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those bathrooms over there, which what bathroom, it was a-- was something with cement done over there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody going pee over there and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we couldn't-- we couldn't have not a little sleep at a time, because every 30 minutes, eight times and more than that, I was getting up, myself and many other people, from the cold because we didn't have no heat over there from the Poland cold, going in those bathrooms.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So how could we go a and work at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why we were hiding, and I could do to go to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And going hiding was afraid that we're going to get killed if they find us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the quarantine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after that, they took us to the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What kind of food did they give you while you were in quarantine?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pfft!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Food, we're not talking about food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Food, losing weight every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The food was kind of radishes, some big radishes like this-- they used to have in Poland and German.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know-- with water because they put into some margarine, I guess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the kitchen, the-- the cooks, they were taking away the-- the margarine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was a kind of a soup, water soup with the radishes, and a little piece, maybe-- maybe two slices of bread, thick like this, with little piece of margarine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was for 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody hungry, and everybody dying from hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We used to call the people they-- they were hungry like this.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
